\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6.3}{\ignorespaces Rendezvous vs Linear Pipeline Performance. (a) Latency comparison showing 1.20$\times $ average latency reduction (65ms $\to $ 54ms) and 2.9$\times $ p50 latency reduction (487ms $\to $ 168ms). Early exit optimization directly reduces average latency by bypassing ML scoring for 13.5\% of records. (b) Throughput comparison showing 2.2$\times $ improvement (8,240 $\to $ 18,450 events/sec) through parallel execution.}}{42}{figure.caption.30}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:exp8a_performance}{{6.3}{42}{Rendezvous vs Linear Pipeline Performance. (a) Latency comparison showing 1.20$\times $ average latency reduction (65ms $\to $ 54ms) and 2.9$\times $ p50 latency reduction (487ms $\to $ 168ms). Early exit optimization directly reduces average latency by bypassing ML scoring for 13.5\% of records. (b) Throughput comparison showing 2.2$\times $ improvement (8,240 $\to $ 18,450 events/sec) through parallel execution}{figure.caption.30}{}}
